</div>
</div></section>

<!-- SEO ARTICLE -->
<section class="article-section">
<div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">GOOD TO KNOW</div>
<h2>Pallet storage: what your business needs to know</h2>
<div class="article-content">
<h3>When you need pallet storage</h3>
<p>Pallet storage is the optimal solution for goods that are stored and moved in full pallets. This includes manufacturers holding finished products before dispatch, importers with container shipments, distributors with transit batches, and e-commerce businesses with large seasonal inventories. If your products weigh more than 20 kg or are kept on standard pallets &mdash; pallet storage is cheaper and more convenient than bin-level storage.</p>

<h3>Address-based racking storage</h3>
<p>Every pallet position at MTP Group has a unique address in the WMS. When a pallet is received, the warehouse operative scans the barcode and the system automatically assigns the optimal racking location based on weight, dimensions and turnover frequency. You can see the exact location of every pallet through your personal dashboard 24/7. Inventory checks are carried out without interrupting operations &mdash; results are available instantly.</p>

<h3>Pallet vs bin storage</h3>
<p>Bin storage (from 650 UAH/m&sup3;/month) is suited for individual items of medium size: cosmetics, electronics, accessories. Pallet storage (from 450 UAH/pallet/month) is for large batches of uniform goods. A common mistake is storing pallet-ready goods in bins &mdash; it takes up more space and costs more. Compare both models by price: <a href="/en/prices/" style="color:var(--red);font-weight:500">storage rates</a>.</p>

<h3>Security and continuity</h3>
<p>The MTP Group warehouse has operated continuously since 2022. Three generators ensure uptime during blackouts. Starlink and two fibre-optic providers guarantee connectivity. Round-the-clock security, full CCTV coverage, temperature control at +5...+25&deg;C. Basic cargo insurance is included &mdash; extended coverage is available on request. See also: <a href="/en/warehouse-services/" style="color:var(--red);font-weight:500">all warehouse services</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

